metadata.name: AI.M #1/2
metadata.description: New perspectives and goals from the success of artificial intelligence "AI" are starting to be widely consumed by the public, with many sectors achieved by AI including the arts sector which ultimately affect the way we live, interact and enhance experiences. Without us knowing it, AI has come and approached us, the spirit of the times to start getting used to side by side or working with AI, which in a short time can learn many things, the impact of which can be good or bad.
